\s YESU MUKIZA WANJE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Yesu Mukiza wanje umv’uko ntakakamba uj’imbere yawe Mwami n’amarira menshi Mwami umbabarire narakosheje rwose nta nicyo nishoboje ungirir’impuhwe. \bd*
\pc \bdit Mwami Yesu unyumve njye munyabyaha pe Unshoboze Mukiza kugera mw’Ijuru.\bdit*\bdit x2\bdit*
